Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:04.60,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fsp4\fade(750,0)\pos(1300,630)}Shiritsu Ebisu Chuugaku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A train bursting at the seams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even during the most unpleasant times
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking of spending the weekend with you would make the time fly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come all this way watching you over a friend's shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So could you praise me for having been able to say that I like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Another scandal in the weekly magazine ads hanging in the train
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to become a lying adult
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we could jump into a world with just the two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In this turbulent age of nothing but fake love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Earnestly, I offer to only you every single bit of my love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If it could be taken away by someone, I'll hold onto it so tight it breaks
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you - do you think could I cling to your arm just a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:02:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing up my hair in a way that matches your preferences
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little lacking in self-confidence as is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I bet you'd get tired of plain cuteness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys are so selfish - have I already lost by falling for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening to that Taylor you like, once again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting a hair dye doesn't sound like a bad idea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I still lose my balance when I don't hold onto the hanging straps
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I now climb the staircase to adulthood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Earnestly, one step at a time, stepping our ground carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:03:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you feel sad, I'll put a smile on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Always right by your side, let's keep holding hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold mine tight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Love, wishes, encounters, building up the future
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The miracle that we, out of 100 million, were bound together
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment that we first kissed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Revealed the reason why we were born
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In this turbulent age of nothing but fake love
